<HL>
   Anti-Crime Bill
   Wins Passage
   In the Senate
   ---
   Measure Includes Provisions
   Aimed at Invigorating
   Probes of Thrift Fraud
   ----
   By Paul M. Barrett
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/12/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
